Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使煙花升起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們請我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為了姐姐這麼努力 真的十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.58,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎麼了 來接我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了…芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 總覺得 願望可能不是這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 芽間覺得也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近電視上放的「非常抖抖」 芽間很喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:20.95,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}「非常抖抖」是日本搞笑藝人樂信吾的一個搞笑段子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:23.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}仁碳你知道「非常抖抖」 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間沒有成佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為願望搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:26.43,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那個人好像超級努力的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要睡的話上去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間正在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓芽間發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得芽間為什麼沒有成佛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為煙花…並不是芽間真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間沒有成佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為願望搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我們有真心為芽間設想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真心想讓芽間實現願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…心裡想的只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想看到仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡一直想著芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望芽間趕緊成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是想要實現她的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了自己而希望芽間成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被神明看透了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使過了這麼長時間 最令我吃驚的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然一成不變地喜歡著她！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 只有宿海能看見芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態…我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不要 讓芽間只屬於宿海一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 倒不如讓她實現願望成佛去就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 最差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子也最差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把心裡話藏起來了！你有話要對雪集說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和前兩天一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個合謀 想弄清仁碳對芽間的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是那樣 我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直嫉妒著芽間 但是你也是一樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因為喜歡雪集 羨慕芽間 才想讓她成佛的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不羨慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一開始我就知道自己比不過芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一樣… 不會做無法實現的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 就算芽間成佛了 代替品也會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算是代替品也沒所謂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…從以前開始就一直羨慕的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 安鳴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那時 還是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是能理解雪集的人 我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我給芽間打小報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她那天你們要追問仁碳的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間知道的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼芽間什麼都不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎麼辦好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆去叫仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間都說要瞞著仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很過分吧？去說說他們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間不止喜歡仁碳…也很喜歡大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我就覺得…自己果然比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然花費了很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我終於成為了能理解雪集的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…我就已經滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在雪集旁邊的也還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓芽間成佛 安鳴和仁碳在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以再…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我最差勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…不可能啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於私心讓芽間成佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的 不管是不是私心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比什麼都不做要好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了 波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不實現芽間的願望的話…不讓她成佛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會原諒我的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看到了 那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃 卻又無法離開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在大家的基地裡 不上高中去環遊世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為跑遠了就能改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回來了 回到那個地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們讓芽間成佛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道這很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這種心情 或許無法讓她成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼前被水沖走 漸漸遠去的芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於芽間的成佛 大家都是帶著私心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而沒有真心地考慮芽間的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 仁太不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在打工嗎 電燈也不關…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天啊 仁太和「超和平Busters」的好朋友們在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的仁太 比以前有活力多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 洗澡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳最近呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳想怎樣都隨他去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好地向芽間道歉 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安…安鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋啦?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！假睫毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我就覺得安鳴的眼睛不一樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠濃密的了 根本沒必要弄假的吧 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴保持這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 謝謝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不准再「安鳴 安鳴」地叫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫回外號了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雪集說的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心 其實在為只有自己能看到芽間而高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 芽間不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 我倒希望她不要成佛的好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只和我 還想和大家一起好好說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要成佛轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地實現芽間的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把芽間也叫來 用日記好好和她談談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芽間一起 再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 芽間不在說什麼都沒有意義 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們六人合在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是「超和平Busters」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是我想說的話啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上把芽間帶過來 去秘密基地集合吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總算開始行動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿自信地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.97,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(379,340)}大結局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.97,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\pos(264,389)}那個夏天盛放的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？怎麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間的願望 好像…已經實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仁碳的媽媽約定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太從來不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為我變成這樣了 所以一直撐著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然轉世投胎也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只有這件事我放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害他一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 我很希望他能多笑一點 多生點氣 多哭一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間和你約定 絕對要讓仁碳哭出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 小芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然芽間考慮了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是完全不知道怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想拜託大家幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是打電話把大家集合起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但並不是讓大家欺負你讓你哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜回到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要實現的…願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間不是很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:46.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不使壞就能把你弄哭的方法 或許大家會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.14,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所以那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為對仁碳保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以遭到懲罰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼懲罰呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會去的 保不保密又有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會去那個地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 又哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 芽間實際上更喜歡仁碳的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到說再見的時間了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的話不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家也是一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很想見你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個…屬於我們的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼突然地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…永遠和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至…想和仁碳一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏是什麼意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 芽間在玩捉迷藏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不可以走…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有…好好地…道別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！芽間!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:58.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間——！芽間——！芽間——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.21,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…稍微等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…差一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 找到芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 芽間已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz40.824\pos(688,133)}仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz348.466\pos(841,293)}波波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz307.74\pos(783,407)}鶴見子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz49.764\pos(469,437)}安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(512,286)}雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…日記的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這字跡…是芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（給鶴見子 最喜歡溫柔的鶴見子了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…間…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（給雪集 最喜歡努力奮鬥的雪集了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（給波波 最喜歡有趣的波波了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（給安鳴 最喜歡可靠的安鳴了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（最喜歡仁碳了 對仁碳的喜歡是 想要成為仁碳新娘的那種喜歡哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次總算…好好地…道別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在玩捉迷藏麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 不把你找出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不算結束了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了沒？藏好了沒？…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經藏好了哦…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…是芽間啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你了 芽間…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 不應該喊名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間還真是不擅長捉迷藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 仁碳 好好說一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…就能結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信 我已經讀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜歡你了 芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜歡你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜歡你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然也最喜歡你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道別 可不能光聽不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望已經達成了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡你了 芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳又把芽間弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭了 弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴老師～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(642,658)}波波你這個叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你這樣不對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想…繼續和大家在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要轉世投胎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新…和大家相聚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…也哭過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…和大家告別了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被找到了…呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著四季交替
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路旁盛開的花兒 也在不斷變化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個季節盛放的花兒 到底叫什麼名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地搖曳著 觸摸它會有點刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子湊過去 會依稀聞到一股青澀的陽光香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著那股香味漸漸變淡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朵花…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還在某處繼續盛放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都將繼續實現 那朵花的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:48.56,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(672,269)}超和平Busters 永遠都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:51.01,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.161\pos(801,510)}Bye Bye
